# ⏱️ Stopwatch & Timer

A modern Stopwatch and Countdown Timer built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It includes stopwatch controls, lap recording, countdown timer, and Local Storage support.

## 🚀 Features

- ▶️ Start Stopwatch
- ⏸️ Pause Stopwatch
- 🔄 Reset Stopwatch
- 🏁 Lap Time
- 💾 Save Lap History
- ⏲️ Countdown Timer
- 🔔 Time's Up Alert
- 📱 Responsive Design

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript
- Local Storage

